WEBVTT

00:00:06.647 --> 00:00:08.348
[<i>Complication</i>

00:00:08.348 --> 00:00:09.850
by ROOKiEZ is PUNK’D]

00:00:09.850 --> 00:00:14.453
♪ ♪

00:00:14.453 --> 00:00:17.455
&gt;&gt; ♪ [singing in Japanese] ♪

00:00:17.455 --> 00:00:25.496
♪ ♪

00:01:06.693 --> 00:01:08.462
&gt;&gt; BY THE WAY, MR. NIEKAWA,

00:01:08.462 --> 00:01:09.463
HOW’S THAT DAUGHTER OF YOURS

00:01:09.463 --> 00:01:09.919
DOING?

00:01:09.919 --> 00:01:11.131
&gt;&gt; SO THEN YOU KNOW NIEKAWA.

00:01:11.131 --> 00:01:12.865
&gt;&gt; OH, JUST HER NAME.

00:01:12.865 --> 00:01:14.834
&gt;&gt; WHO’S HARUNA NIEKAWA?

00:01:14.834 --> 00:01:16.535
&gt;&gt; THAT’S RIDICULOUS.

00:01:16.535 --> 00:01:18.503
SHIZUO’S WAY STRONGER THAN I AM.

00:01:18.503 --> 00:01:19.570
&gt;&gt; THIS IS THE PERSON THAT’S

00:01:19.570 --> 00:01:20.838
BEEN TROLLING OUR FORUM FOR,

00:01:20.838 --> 00:01:22.105
LIKE, THE PAST SIX MONTHS,

00:01:22.105 --> 00:01:23.841
RIGHT?

00:01:23.841 --> 00:01:24.541
&gt;&gt; RUN!

00:01:24.541 --> 00:01:26.843
&gt;&gt; I LOVE YOU SO, SO, SO, SO,

00:01:26.843 --> 00:01:28.510
SO, SO MUCH, SHIZUO.

00:01:28.510 --> 00:01:31.513
&gt;&gt; ♪ [singing in Japanese] ♪

00:01:31.513 --> 00:01:39.553
♪ ♪

00:01:58.634 --> 00:02:01.102
&gt;&gt; [pants maniacally]

00:02:01.102 --> 00:02:02.403
&gt;&gt; HUH.

00:02:02.403 --> 00:02:03.604
KYOHEI,

00:02:03.604 --> 00:02:06.474
I’M BORROWING YOUR DOOR.

00:02:07.741 --> 00:02:09.442
[grunts with effort]

00:02:09.442 --> 00:02:11.477
&gt;&gt; both: WHOA!

00:02:14.580 --> 00:02:15.413
&gt;&gt; [sighs]

00:02:15.413 --> 00:02:17.682
&gt;&gt; [groans and wails]

00:02:17.682 --> 00:02:19.484
&gt;&gt; UGH!

00:02:19.484 --> 00:02:20.751
[charging yell]

00:02:20.751 --> 00:02:21.718
AH!

00:02:21.718 --> 00:02:23.453
&gt;&gt; [whimpers]

00:02:25.121 --> 00:02:26.989
&gt;&gt; all: [gasp]

00:02:26.989 --> 00:02:29.424
&gt;&gt; SO WHO DO I GET TO BUY ME A

00:02:29.424 --> 00:02:32.527
NEW DOOR?

00:02:36.897 --> 00:02:38.832
&gt;&gt; WHEN I GOT BACK, I TOLD

00:02:38.832 --> 00:02:41.166
SHINRA WHAT HAD HAPPENED...

00:02:41.166 --> 00:02:44.136
THAT IT WAS ALL OVER NOW.

00:02:44.136 --> 00:02:45.904
&gt;&gt; BUT IT WASN’T OVER.

00:02:45.904 --> 00:02:49.072
IN FACT, IT WAS JUST BEGINNING.

00:02:49.072 --> 00:02:51.508
&gt;&gt; IT WAS A VERY LONG NIGHT.

00:02:51.508 --> 00:02:53.010
THE GUY WHO ATTACKED US WAS

00:02:53.010 --> 00:02:54.644
STILL OUT COLD, SO I LEFT HIM

00:02:54.644 --> 00:02:55.778
WITH KYOHEI AND THE OTHERS

00:02:55.778 --> 00:02:56.812
WHILE I TOOK THE GIRL HOME.

00:02:56.812 --> 00:02:58.214
&gt;&gt; [sniffs]

00:02:58.214 --> 00:02:59.681
&gt;&gt; THIS IS THE GIRL WHO HANGS

00:02:59.681 --> 00:03:00.949
OUT WITH MIKADO.

00:03:00.949 --> 00:03:02.750
BEFORE WE LEFT, SHE ASKED TO SEE

00:03:02.750 --> 00:03:04.618
IF I REALLY DIDN’T HAVE A HEAD.

00:03:04.618 --> 00:03:06.053
&gt;&gt; SO YOU SHOWED HER?

00:03:06.053 --> 00:03:08.487
&gt;&gt; YES, AND LIKE MIKADO, SHE

00:03:08.487 --> 00:03:10.023
WASN’T SURPRISED.

00:03:10.023 --> 00:03:11.123
MAYBE THAT’S JUST HOW KIDS ARE

00:03:11.123 --> 00:03:11.924
THESE DAYS.

00:03:11.924 --> 00:03:13.191
&gt;&gt; DOUBT IT.

00:03:13.191 --> 00:03:14.159
I DON’T THINK BEING A KID HAS

00:03:14.159 --> 00:03:17.194
ANYTHING TO DO WITH IT.

00:03:23.599 --> 00:03:24.200
[doorbell rings]

00:03:24.200 --> 00:03:27.669
&gt;&gt; [starts] HUH?

00:03:27.669 --> 00:03:29.771
&gt;&gt; IS THAT CELTY?

00:03:34.842 --> 00:03:35.642
[doorbell rings]

00:03:35.642 --> 00:03:40.779
&gt;&gt; [starts]

00:03:40.779 --> 00:03:43.081
HUH?

00:03:46.551 --> 00:03:49.586
UM, EXCUSE ME, BUT WHO ARE YOU?

00:03:49.586 --> 00:03:52.188
&gt;&gt; GOOD EVENING, ANRI.

00:03:52.188 --> 00:03:56.825
MY NAME’S HARUNA NIEKAWA.

00:03:59.627 --> 00:04:00.662
&gt;&gt; SO THAT’S IT.

00:04:00.662 --> 00:04:02.029
THAT’S ALL THAT HAPPENED.

00:04:02.029 --> 00:04:03.530
THANKS FOR LOOKING INTO SAIKA,

00:04:03.530 --> 00:04:04.965
BUT I THINK IT’S OVER NOW.

00:04:04.965 --> 00:04:07.267
&gt;&gt; YEAH, MAYBE, BUT YOU KNOW,

00:04:07.267 --> 00:04:08.768
IT SEEMS A LITTLE TOO

00:04:08.768 --> 00:04:11.903
ANTI-CLIMACTIC FOR ME, TOO EASY.

00:04:11.903 --> 00:04:13.137
&gt;&gt; SO WHAT ARE WE SUPPOSED TO DO

00:04:13.137 --> 00:04:14.038
WITH THIS GUY?

00:04:14.038 --> 00:04:15.506
&gt;&gt; WELL, WE SHOULD CALL AN

00:04:15.506 --> 00:04:16.240
AMBULANCE, I GUESS.

00:04:16.240 --> 00:04:17.508
&gt;&gt; YOU KNOW WHAT?

00:04:17.508 --> 00:04:18.508
&gt;&gt; all: HUH?

00:04:18.508 --> 00:04:19.276
&gt;&gt; [inhales]

00:04:19.276 --> 00:04:20.943
SOMETHING JUST DOESN’T FEEL

00:04:20.943 --> 00:04:22.512
RIGHT TO ME.

00:04:22.512 --> 00:04:25.047
WHY IS THAT?

00:04:25.047 --> 00:04:26.582
I’M OFF TO SHINJUKU TO KILL

00:04:26.582 --> 00:04:27.616
IZAYA.

00:04:27.616 --> 00:04:29.984
I’LL BE BACK.

00:04:29.984 --> 00:04:32.019
&gt;&gt; OH, MAN, THIS IS SO COOL!

00:04:32.019 --> 00:04:33.620
SHIZU-CHAN TOTALLY HAS THE HOTS

00:04:33.620 --> 00:04:34.221
FOR IZAYA.

00:04:34.221 --> 00:04:35.021
&gt;&gt; all: HUH?

00:04:35.021 --> 00:04:35.922
&gt;&gt; BOY-ON-BOY LOVE IS SO MUCH

00:04:35.922 --> 00:04:36.589
FUN.

00:04:36.589 --> 00:04:37.056
I LOVE IT!

00:04:37.056 --> 00:04:37.923
&gt;&gt; all: NOT HAPPENIN’.

00:04:37.923 --> 00:04:38.657
&gt;&gt; HUH?

00:04:38.657 --> 00:04:40.125
&gt;&gt; YOU KNOW, SHE MIGHT BE--

00:04:40.125 --> 00:04:41.960
&gt;&gt; NO, JUST THE THOUGHT OF THOSE

00:04:41.960 --> 00:04:43.295
TWO TOGETHER IS WRONG.

00:04:43.295 --> 00:04:44.095
&gt;&gt; HMM.

00:04:44.095 --> 00:04:46.963
&gt;&gt; ANYWAY, HERE IT IS.

00:04:52.302 --> 00:04:54.103
JUST DON’T TOUCH IT.

00:04:54.103 --> 00:04:57.071
IT MIGHT POSSESS YOU.

00:04:57.071 --> 00:05:00.074
&gt;&gt; HMM.

00:05:00.074 --> 00:05:02.242
[otherworldly unraveling]

00:05:02.242 --> 00:05:04.644
&gt;&gt; THIS IS SAIKA?

00:05:04.644 --> 00:05:06.178
A BUTCHER KNIFE?

00:05:06.178 --> 00:05:08.080
&gt;&gt; IT SURPRISED ME, TOO, BUT

00:05:08.080 --> 00:05:09.548
THE GUY HOLDING IT HAD THE

00:05:09.548 --> 00:05:10.649
GLOWING, RED EYES AND A

00:05:10.649 --> 00:05:11.582
HIGH-PITCHED VOICE.

00:05:11.582 --> 00:05:13.551
HE SOUNDED LIKE A WOMAN, AND HE

00:05:13.551 --> 00:05:15.620
KEPT SPOUTING CRAZY NONSENSE

00:05:15.620 --> 00:05:16.753
ABOUT LOVE OR SOMETHING.

00:05:16.753 --> 00:05:17.854
&gt;&gt; WELL, NOW.

00:05:17.854 --> 00:05:19.656
LOVE, HUH?

00:05:19.656 --> 00:05:20.689
&gt;&gt; I FEEL LIKE I’VE SEEN THAT

00:05:20.689 --> 00:05:22.758
GUY SOMEWHERE BEFORE.

00:05:22.758 --> 00:05:24.893
REGARDLESS, HOW DOES LOVE HAVE

00:05:24.893 --> 00:05:26.928
ANYTHING TO DO WITH SLASHING?

00:05:26.928 --> 00:05:28.930
IS SAIKA SOME KIND OF SADIST?

00:05:28.930 --> 00:05:30.731
&gt;&gt; NO, I DON’T THINK SADIST IS

00:05:30.731 --> 00:05:32.032
THE WORD YOU’RE LOOKING FOR.

00:05:32.032 --> 00:05:32.999
AHEM.

00:05:32.999 --> 00:05:34.934
SEE, SAIKA’S DESIRE IS

00:05:34.934 --> 00:05:38.337
ULTIMATELY TO LOVE PEOPLE.

00:05:38.337 --> 00:05:40.305
THAT BLADE HAS BEEN INFATUATED

00:05:40.305 --> 00:05:42.306
WITH THE HUMAN RACE FOR SO LONG

00:05:42.306 --> 00:05:43.641
THAT IT STOPPED SEEING PEOPLE AS

00:05:43.641 --> 00:05:45.676
INDIVIDUALS, AND NOW IT’S

00:05:45.676 --> 00:05:47.310
OBSESSED WITH HUMANITY...

00:05:47.310 --> 00:05:48.811
ALL OF HUMANITY.

00:05:48.811 --> 00:05:50.279
&gt;&gt; I DON’T UNDERSTAND.

00:05:50.279 --> 00:05:51.813
IF IT LOVES PEOPLE, WHY SLASH

00:05:51.813 --> 00:05:52.648
THEM?

00:05:52.648 --> 00:05:55.016
&gt;&gt; [uncomfortable sigh]

00:05:55.016 --> 00:05:56.217
&gt;&gt; SO ANRI...

00:05:56.217 --> 00:05:57.152
&gt;&gt; [whimpers]

00:05:57.152 --> 00:05:58.686
&gt;&gt; I DECIDED TO COME HERE AND

00:05:58.686 --> 00:06:00.287
PAY YOU A VISIT TONIGHT.

00:06:00.287 --> 00:06:01.721
KNOW WHY?

00:06:01.721 --> 00:06:02.822
&gt;&gt; IS IT BECAUSE OF THAT

00:06:02.822 --> 00:06:06.325
TEACHER, MR. NASUJIMA?

00:06:06.325 --> 00:06:07.793
I DON’T KNOW WHAT YOU’VE HEARD,

00:06:07.793 --> 00:06:09.027
BUT I’VE HAD NOTHING TO DO WITH

00:06:09.027 --> 00:06:10.062
HIM.

00:06:10.062 --> 00:06:11.629
THOSE ARE JUST RUMORS PEOPLE ARE

00:06:11.629 --> 00:06:12.363
SPREADING.

00:06:12.363 --> 00:06:14.731
&gt;&gt; OH, I KNOW THAT.

00:06:14.731 --> 00:06:16.767
&gt;&gt; [sighs]

00:06:16.767 --> 00:06:19.001
&gt;&gt; BUT YOU SEE, I LOVE TAKASHI.

00:06:19.001 --> 00:06:21.136
&gt;&gt; HUH?

00:06:21.136 --> 00:06:22.637
&gt;&gt; WHEN PEOPLE ARE IN LOVE, THEY

00:06:22.637 --> 00:06:23.938
HAVE VARIOUS WAYS IN WHICH THEY

00:06:23.938 --> 00:06:25.640
TRY TO EXPRESS THAT EMOTION,

00:06:25.640 --> 00:06:26.374
RIGHT?

00:06:26.374 --> 00:06:28.041
&gt;&gt; WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

00:06:28.041 --> 00:06:29.710
&gt;&gt; LIKE HOLDING HANDS, OR

00:06:29.710 --> 00:06:31.778
EMBRACING, OR EVEN TALKING.

00:06:31.778 --> 00:06:33.613
&gt;&gt; SO THE TWO OF YOU WERE

00:06:33.613 --> 00:06:34.614
DATING, THEN?

00:06:34.614 --> 00:06:35.881
&gt;&gt; IT WAS MORE THAN JUST SIMPLE

00:06:35.881 --> 00:06:36.882
DATING.

00:06:36.882 --> 00:06:39.684
THE TWO OF US WERE IN LOVE,

00:06:39.684 --> 00:06:41.652
AND KNOWING THAT WAS ALL THE

00:06:41.652 --> 00:06:43.120
HAPPINESS BOTH OF US EVER

00:06:43.120 --> 00:06:44.388
NEEDED.

00:06:44.388 --> 00:06:47.023
YES, WE WERE GONNA BE TOGETHER

00:06:47.023 --> 00:06:48.925
FOREVER...

00:06:48.925 --> 00:06:52.795
BUT THEN ONE DAY HE REJECTED ME.

00:06:52.795 --> 00:06:54.729
I DON’T KNOW WHY.

00:06:54.729 --> 00:06:55.763
I JUST WANTED TO SHOW HIM I

00:06:55.763 --> 00:06:56.664
REALLY LOVE HIM.

00:06:56.664 --> 00:06:58.065
&gt;&gt; MM.

00:06:58.065 --> 00:07:01.134
SO THEN, WHAT DID YOU DO TO

00:07:01.134 --> 00:07:02.368
PROVE IT TO HIM?

00:07:02.368 --> 00:07:04.804
[gulps]

00:07:04.804 --> 00:07:06.271
&gt;&gt; AT SOME POINT, SAIKA BEGAN

00:07:06.271 --> 00:07:07.672
WANTING TO EXPRESS ITS LOVE

00:07:07.672 --> 00:07:09.073
THROUGH ACTIONS, BUT SAIKA’S

00:07:09.073 --> 00:07:11.642
JUST A SWORD; IT HAS NO BODY.

00:07:11.642 --> 00:07:13.110
&gt;&gt; SO IT USES THE BODY OF

00:07:13.110 --> 00:07:14.211
WHOEVER’S POSSESSING IT.

00:07:14.211 --> 00:07:15.678
&gt;&gt; AND THEN IT STARTS SLASHING

00:07:15.678 --> 00:07:17.880
PEOPLE, OVER AND OVER AGAIN,

00:07:17.880 --> 00:07:19.081
TRYING TO ILLUSTRATE WHAT IT

00:07:19.081 --> 00:07:20.982
FEELS.

00:07:20.982 --> 00:07:22.417
&gt;&gt; IT WANTS ITS LOVE TO HAVE

00:07:22.417 --> 00:07:24.685
TANGIBLE FORM.

00:07:24.685 --> 00:07:26.854
&gt;&gt; TAKASHI SPURNED MY LOVE.

00:07:26.854 --> 00:07:29.789
THAT’S FINE, REALLY, I DON’T

00:07:29.789 --> 00:07:31.758
HATE HIM FOR THAT.

00:07:31.758 --> 00:07:33.392
YOU SEE, THERE’S NO WAY I COULD

00:07:33.392 --> 00:07:35.327
EVER HATE HIM, BECAUSE I TRULY

00:07:35.327 --> 00:07:36.361
LOVE HIM.

00:07:36.361 --> 00:07:38.430
&gt;&gt; OKAY, WELL, THEN--

00:07:38.430 --> 00:07:40.164
&gt;&gt; EVEN IF HE NEVER COMES BACK

00:07:40.164 --> 00:07:41.999
TO ME, IF HE CHOOSES SOMEONE

00:07:41.999 --> 00:07:44.200
ELSE, THAT’S FINE.

00:07:44.200 --> 00:07:46.669
I’LL FORGIVE HIM.

00:07:46.669 --> 00:07:47.703
HOWEVER...

00:07:47.703 --> 00:07:49.371
&gt;&gt; [whimpers]

00:07:49.371 --> 00:07:50.839
&gt;&gt; IF SOMEONE TAKES TAKASHI’S

00:07:50.839 --> 00:07:54.208
LOVE, I WON’T FORGIVE THEM, NOT

00:07:54.208 --> 00:07:55.376
EVER.

00:07:55.376 --> 00:07:56.277
&gt;&gt; [whimpers]

00:07:56.277 --> 00:07:58.245
&gt;&gt; ABOUT FIVE YEARS AGO, SAIKA

00:07:58.245 --> 00:08:00.347
SEEMED TO HAVE DISAPPEARED, BUT

00:08:00.347 --> 00:08:01.714
FROM WHAT I’VE SEEN IN THAT CHAT

00:08:01.714 --> 00:08:03.749
ROOM, I’D SAY THAT BLADE IS

00:08:03.749 --> 00:08:05.250
STILL VERY MUCH ALIVE, AND IN

00:08:05.250 --> 00:08:06.852
LOVE.

00:08:06.852 --> 00:08:09.687
&gt;&gt; WAIT, SHINRA, I REMEMBER NOW.

00:08:09.687 --> 00:08:10.721
I KNEW I’D MET THAT GUY WITH THE

00:08:10.721 --> 00:08:12.022
KNIFE SOMEWHERE BEFORE.

00:08:12.022 --> 00:08:13.223
HE’S A REPORTER.

00:08:13.223 --> 00:08:14.924
HIS NAME IS...

00:08:14.924 --> 00:08:16.192
&gt;&gt; I’VE LEARNED THAT YOU CAN’T

00:08:16.192 --> 00:08:18.327
ALWAYS RELY ON HUMANS.

00:08:18.327 --> 00:08:19.995
IT JUST GOES TO SHOW, IF YOU

00:08:19.995 --> 00:08:21.229
WANT TO PROVE YOUR LOVE, THEN

00:08:21.229 --> 00:08:22.397
YOU SHOULD GO AND DO IT

00:08:22.397 --> 00:08:23.865
YOURSELF.

00:08:23.865 --> 00:08:25.199
&gt;&gt; [grunts]

00:08:25.199 --> 00:08:27.133
&gt;&gt; I MUST SAY, I THOUGHT FOR

00:08:27.133 --> 00:08:28.334
SURE MY FATHER WOULD DO A BETTER

00:08:28.334 --> 00:08:30.736
JOB THAN THE OTHERS DID, BUT

00:08:30.736 --> 00:08:32.471
CLEARLY I WAS WRONG.

00:08:32.471 --> 00:08:34.473
SO I’LL DO THE JOB MYSELF.

00:08:34.473 --> 00:08:36.408
I WILL TAKE CARE OF THINGS ON MY

00:08:36.408 --> 00:08:37.876
OWN...

00:08:37.876 --> 00:08:40.778
WITH YOU, MY NEMESIS.

00:08:40.778 --> 00:08:43.413
&gt;&gt; SO THAT MAN, HE WAS YOUR

00:08:43.413 --> 00:08:44.281
FATHER?

00:08:44.281 --> 00:08:45.314
&gt;&gt; [groans]

00:08:45.314 --> 00:08:47.316
UGH.

00:08:47.316 --> 00:08:49.985
&gt;&gt; THAT WAS SHUJI NIEKAWA.

00:08:49.985 --> 00:08:51.252
HE’S THE GUY WHO WAS ATTACKED

00:08:51.252 --> 00:08:52.287
RIGHT IN FRONT OF HIS HOUSE.

00:08:52.287 --> 00:08:55.289
&gt;&gt; HMM, WHY WOULD IT DO THAT?

00:08:55.289 --> 00:08:57.424
UH, WHAT THE--

00:08:57.424 --> 00:09:01.394
WHAT?

00:09:01.394 --> 00:09:03.295
&gt;&gt; WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

00:09:03.295 --> 00:09:05.330
SO DO YOU FEEL ANYTHING?

00:09:05.330 --> 00:09:06.764
DOES IT SEEM LIKE SOMETHING’S

00:09:06.764 --> 00:09:08.165
TRYING TO POSSESS YOU?

00:09:08.165 --> 00:09:09.766
&gt;&gt; NO, NOT AT ALL.

00:09:09.766 --> 00:09:11.334
THIS ISN’T SAIKA.

00:09:11.334 --> 00:09:13.769
HERE, SEE FOR YOURSELF.

00:09:18.207 --> 00:09:19.441
THERE’S NO WAY THAT A LEGENDARY

00:09:19.441 --> 00:09:20.975
BLADE WHOSE HISTORY GOES BACK

00:09:20.975 --> 00:09:22.343
FOR DECADES WOULD SAY, "MADE IN

00:09:22.343 --> 00:09:25.078
2009."

00:09:25.078 --> 00:09:26.113
[taps on phone]

00:09:26.113 --> 00:09:28.114
&gt;&gt; HOW CAN THAT BE?

00:09:28.114 --> 00:09:29.381
LISTEN, I KNOW WHAT I SAW,

00:09:29.381 --> 00:09:30.416
BELIEVE ME.

00:09:30.416 --> 00:09:31.450
&gt;&gt; I BELIEVE YOU.

00:09:31.450 --> 00:09:32.918
I PROMISE, I WOULD NEVER DOUBT

00:09:32.918 --> 00:09:34.285
YOU.

00:09:34.285 --> 00:09:36.487
MAYBE THIS NIEKAWA GUY STUMBLED

00:09:36.487 --> 00:09:38.522
UPON THE SAIKA LEGEND AND TRIED

00:09:38.522 --> 00:09:39.823
TO COPY IT.

00:09:39.823 --> 00:09:40.424
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

00:09:40.424 --> 00:09:41.825
&gt;&gt; I THINK THE BIGGER ISSUE IS,

00:09:41.825 --> 00:09:43.392
IF THIS ISN’T SAIKA--

00:09:43.392 --> 00:09:44.960
&gt;&gt; THEN SAIKA’S STILL OUT THERE

00:09:44.960 --> 00:09:47.095
SOMEWHERE, WHICH MEANS CHANCES

00:09:47.095 --> 00:09:48.930
ARE, IT’S STILL POSSESSING

00:09:48.930 --> 00:09:51.332
SOMEONE AND ATTACKING PEOPLE.

00:09:51.332 --> 00:09:52.967
&gt;&gt; HOW ABOUT THE CHAT ROOM?

00:09:52.967 --> 00:09:56.136
HAS IT BEEN THERE LATELY?

00:09:59.271 --> 00:10:01.173
&gt;&gt; BUT I TOLD YOU, I DON’T CARE

00:10:01.173 --> 00:10:03.107
ABOUT NASUJIMA, I PROMISE.

00:10:03.107 --> 00:10:04.508
&gt;&gt; THAT’S QUITE ALL RIGHT.

00:10:04.508 --> 00:10:06.044
I DON’T CARE HOW YOU FEEL ABOUT

00:10:06.044 --> 00:10:06.844
HIM.

00:10:06.844 --> 00:10:08.045
THAT’S NOT WHY I’M HERE.

00:10:08.045 --> 00:10:09.346
I’M HERE BECAUSE I’M DOING WHAT

00:10:09.346 --> 00:10:11.214
I HAVE TO DO IN ORDER TO PROVE

