00:19:05.193 --> 00:19:07.227
MAKE ONE THING CLEAR.

00:19:07.227 --> 00:19:09.229
NONE OF YOU ARE MY TYPE.

00:19:09.229 --> 00:19:11.398
NEVER HAVE BEEN, AND NEVER WILL

00:19:11.398 --> 00:19:12.331
BE.

00:19:12.331 --> 00:19:15.668
I HATE YOU GUYS, ALMOST AS MUCH

00:19:15.668 --> 00:19:16.969
AS IZAYA.

00:19:16.969 --> 00:19:18.370
[charging yell]

00:19:19.671 --> 00:19:21.472
&gt;&gt; SHINRA, SOMETHING ELSE STILL

00:19:21.472 --> 00:19:22.806
BOTHERS ME.

00:19:22.806 --> 00:19:24.808
YOU SAID SAIKA DISAPPEARED FIVE

00:19:24.808 --> 00:19:26.943
YEARS AGO, RIGHT?

00:19:26.943 --> 00:19:28.578
WHY IS THAT?

00:19:28.578 --> 00:19:31.880
WHAT HAPPENED FIVE YEARS AGO?

00:19:31.880 --> 00:19:33.715
&gt;&gt; WELL, I HIGHLY DOUBT IT CHOSE

00:19:33.715 --> 00:19:35.483
TO TAKE A VACATION.

00:19:35.483 --> 00:19:37.250
IT’S POSSIBLE THAT SOMEONE VERY

00:19:37.250 --> 00:19:39.352
STRONG CAME IN CONTACT WITH IT

00:19:39.352 --> 00:19:40.453
AND HAS SOMEHOW MANAGED TO

00:19:40.453 --> 00:19:41.454
SUPPRESS IT.

00:19:41.454 --> 00:19:42.388
[pants in fear]

00:19:42.388 --> 00:19:43.755
&gt;&gt; WHO WOULD THAT BE?

00:19:43.755 --> 00:19:45.624
&gt;&gt; I’VE THOUGHT ABOUT YOU FOR SO

00:19:45.624 --> 00:19:46.492
LONG.

00:19:46.492 --> 00:19:48.359
I KNOW YOU LOVED ME AS MUCH AS I

00:19:48.359 --> 00:19:49.360
LOVED YOU.

00:19:49.360 --> 00:19:50.795
YOU SHOWED THAT IN THE WAY YOU

00:19:50.795 --> 00:19:52.629
TRIED TO EXTORT MONEY FROM ME,

00:19:52.629 --> 00:19:54.464
AND HOW YOU TRIED TO ABANDON ME,

00:19:54.464 --> 00:19:55.665
ONCE YOU GOT BORED.

00:19:55.665 --> 00:19:57.433
AND NO MATTER WHAT, I ACCEPTED

00:19:57.433 --> 00:19:59.301
YOU, I LOVED AND FORGAVE YOU.

00:19:59.301 --> 00:20:01.369
&gt;&gt; [whimpers]

00:20:01.369 --> 00:20:03.505
&gt;&gt; BUT STILL, THAT JUST WASN’T

00:20:03.505 --> 00:20:04.305
ENOUGH.

00:20:04.305 --> 00:20:05.940
NO, THAT WASN’T EVEN CLOSE TO

00:20:05.940 --> 00:20:07.774
ENOUGH.

00:20:07.774 --> 00:20:10.376
ENTER SAIKA.

00:20:10.376 --> 00:20:11.877
SHE STARTED SPEAKING TO ME AND

00:20:11.877 --> 00:20:13.412
TELLING ME THINGS.

00:20:13.412 --> 00:20:14.446
&gt;&gt; [pants in fear]

00:20:14.446 --> 00:20:17.015
&gt;&gt; THINGS LIKE THIS.

00:20:17.015 --> 00:20:19.383
AND THAT’S HOW SHE SPEAKS, WITH

00:20:19.383 --> 00:20:21.452
ME GIVING HER MORE BLOOD.

00:20:21.452 --> 00:20:22.820
SEE?

00:20:22.820 --> 00:20:23.920
&gt;&gt; [whimpers]

00:20:23.920 --> 00:20:27.823
&gt;&gt; SO WILL YOU TAKE MY LOVE?

00:20:27.823 --> 00:20:29.425
I REALLY DO WANT TO GIVE IT TO

00:20:29.425 --> 00:20:31.760
YOU.

00:20:31.760 --> 00:20:32.560
&gt;&gt; [whimpers]

00:20:32.560 --> 00:20:33.561
[terrified gasp]

00:20:33.561 --> 00:20:34.462
[whimpers]

00:20:34.462 --> 00:20:35.462
[screams]

00:20:35.462 --> 00:20:36.463
&gt;&gt; WAIT!

00:20:36.463 --> 00:20:37.464
&gt;&gt; OH.

00:20:37.464 --> 00:20:40.733
&gt;&gt; [panting] HARUNA...

00:20:40.733 --> 00:20:43.702
PLEASE, YOU HAVE TO STOP THIS.

00:20:43.702 --> 00:20:45.403
STOP HURTING PEOPLE WITH THAT

00:20:45.403 --> 00:20:46.504
KNIFE!

00:20:46.504 --> 00:20:47.772
&gt;&gt; HOW DID YOU GET OUT OF THERE

00:20:47.772 --> 00:20:49.473
ALIVE?

00:20:49.473 --> 00:20:52.743
&gt;&gt; PLEASE STOP.

00:20:52.743 --> 00:20:54.944
&gt;&gt; FINE, WHATEVER.

00:20:54.944 --> 00:20:56.412
I’M GUESSING THAT SOMEONE CAME

00:20:56.412 --> 00:20:57.780
IN AND SAVED YOU AGAIN.

00:20:57.780 --> 00:20:59.914
NOW, LISTEN, I REALLY DON’T LIKE

00:20:59.914 --> 00:21:01.449
YOU COMING HERE, AND TELLING ME

00:21:01.449 --> 00:21:03.284
WHAT I SHOULD DO.

00:21:03.284 --> 00:21:04.918
I DON’T NEED ADVICE FROM SOMEONE

00:21:04.918 --> 00:21:06.419
SO WEAK, THAT THEY LEECH OFF OF

00:21:06.419 --> 00:21:07.420
OTHERS.

00:21:07.420 --> 00:21:08.388
&gt;&gt; YOU HAVE IT WRONG.

00:21:08.388 --> 00:21:09.422
I DIDN’T DO IT BECAUSE I WAS

00:21:09.422 --> 00:21:11.423
WEAK, I HAD OTHER OPTIONS.

00:21:11.423 --> 00:21:13.492
I CHOSE THIS LIFE FOR A REASON,

00:21:13.492 --> 00:21:14.926
NOT BECAUSE I HAD TO.

00:21:14.926 --> 00:21:16.727
&gt;&gt; HUH, SAME THING.

00:21:16.727 --> 00:21:18.463
&gt;&gt; YOU CAN’T JUDGE PEOPLE BY HOW

00:21:18.463 --> 00:21:20.497
THEY LIVE AND JUST DECIDE IF

00:21:20.497 --> 00:21:21.698
THEY’RE WEAK OR STRONG.

00:21:21.698 --> 00:21:24.567
&gt;&gt; SO TELL ME SOMETHING--HAVE

00:21:24.567 --> 00:21:25.968
YOU EVER ACTUALLY LOVED SOMEONE

00:21:25.968 --> 00:21:26.769
BEFORE?

00:21:26.769 --> 00:21:27.770
&gt;&gt; [cries]

00:21:27.770 --> 00:21:29.904
&gt;&gt; NO, I DON’T THINK YOU HAVE.

00:21:29.904 --> 00:21:31.939
SO IT GOES TO SAY, YOU CAN’T

00:21:31.939 --> 00:21:33.540
UNDERSTAND ME.

00:21:33.540 --> 00:21:35.909
LISTEN CLOSE, I WAS ABLE TO TAKE

00:21:35.909 --> 00:21:37.677
OVER SAIKA WITH THE POWER OF MY

00:21:37.677 --> 00:21:39.011
LOVE.

00:21:39.011 --> 00:21:40.613
THE FIRST TIME SAIKA TOLD ME TO

00:21:40.613 --> 00:21:41.881
CUT TAKASHI, I RESISTED WITH

00:21:41.881 --> 00:21:43.015
EVERYTHING I HAD.

00:21:43.015 --> 00:21:45.449
BUT THEN, AS I LISTENED TO HER

00:21:45.449 --> 00:21:48.619
VOICE, I UNDERSTOOD...

00:21:48.619 --> 00:21:50.587
AND THAT’S WHY SAIKA AND I HAVE

00:21:50.587 --> 00:21:51.621
BECOME THE MOTHER.

00:21:51.621 --> 00:21:53.590
WE’RE MAKING AS MANY CHILDREN AS

00:21:53.590 --> 00:21:54.991
WE POSSIBLY CAN IN AN EFFORT

00:21:54.991 --> 00:21:56.558
TO SPREAD OUR LOVE.

00:21:56.558 --> 00:21:57.659
THAT’S RIGHT, LOVE!

00:21:57.659 --> 00:21:58.960
SOMEDAY WE WILL LOVE AND

00:21:58.960 --> 00:22:02.563
CONTROL THE ENTIRE HUMAN RACE!

00:22:02.563 --> 00:22:03.798
[charging yell]

00:22:05.432 --> 00:22:06.032
[grunts]

00:22:06.032 --> 00:22:07.033
[metallic impact]

00:22:07.033 --> 00:22:08.067
&gt;&gt; [grunts with effort]

00:22:09.768 --> 00:22:12.037
&gt;&gt; [gasps]

00:22:12.037 --> 00:22:13.371
&gt;&gt; YOU’RE RIGHT.

00:22:13.371 --> 00:22:14.572
IT’S LIKE YOU SAID.

00:22:14.572 --> 00:22:16.607
I CAN’T LOVE ANYONE.

00:22:16.607 --> 00:22:17.874
I’VE BEEN TOO SCARED...

00:22:17.874 --> 00:22:20.043
EVER SINCE THAT DAY FIVE YEARS

00:22:20.043 --> 00:22:21.744
AGO.

00:22:21.744 --> 00:22:24.647
AND THAT’S WHY I CHOOSE TO RELY

00:22:24.647 --> 00:22:25.447
ON OTHERS.

00:22:25.447 --> 00:22:27.616
&gt;&gt; THIS CAN’T BE!

00:22:27.616 --> 00:22:28.717
&gt;&gt; YOU WERE ABLE TO MAKE

00:22:28.717 --> 00:22:30.451
CHILDREN BY SLASHING OTHERS WITH

00:22:30.451 --> 00:22:32.753
THAT BLADE, BUT YOUR SAIKA IS

00:22:32.753 --> 00:22:35.755
JUST ANOTHER CHILD, TOO.

00:22:35.755 --> 00:22:37.557
THE MOTHER OF ALL THOSE BLADES

00:22:37.557 --> 00:22:38.925
IS THIS.

00:22:38.925 --> 00:22:39.891
&gt;&gt; [gasps]

00:22:39.891 --> 00:22:41.327
&gt;&gt; OH.

00:22:44.562 --> 00:22:47.564
&gt;&gt; I AM UNABLE TO LOVE, AND THIS

00:22:47.564 --> 00:22:48.932
IS THE REASON...

00:22:48.932 --> 00:22:50.634
THAT I MUST RELY ON SAIKA TO

00:22:50.634 --> 00:22:52.668
LOVE OTHER PEOPLE FOR ME.

00:22:52.668 --> 00:22:56.538
YOU SEE, I TRULY AM HER

00:22:56.538 --> 00:22:58.973
PARASITE.

